Subject: net/smc: Use active link of the connection
Git-commit: 8b2f0f44f06bd5f00d7d5e6c20a4dc3ec28e0ecd
Patch-mainline: v5.11-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-15862 bsc#1180744 LTC#186340

Use active link of the connection directly and not
via linkgroup array structure when obtaining link
data of the connection.

